           CoreFPGA User&apos;s Manual MD00116-2B-COREFPGA-USM-01.00.pdf
           Linux for the MIPS Malta Development Platform User&apos;s Guide MD00646-2B-LINUXMALTA-USM-01.03.pdf"/>
    </docsection>
